OL,3,COne of the smallest young farmers'
OL,4,Cclubs in Wales vying to be Best in
OL,5,CBritain
OL,7,FWith just 27 members, Ystradfellte YFC
OL,8,Fis one of the smallest young farmers'
OL,9,Fclubs in the UK, but they have been
OL,10,Fshortlisted for Best in Britain 2024'.
OL,12,FIt is one of three clubs bidding for
OL,13,Fthe title, and its members will be
OL,14,Fheading to Yorkshire to find out who's
OL,15,Fwon at the end of August.
OL,17,FSpeaking to ITV Cymru Wales about how
OL,18,Fthey felt about being shortlisted, one
OL,19,Fmember said: "Just excited, over the
OL,20,Fmoon really! No words can describe it."
