OL,7,FAnother said they were "gobsmacked".
OL,9,F"As much as I love the club, I was
OL,10,Fshocked! We're such a small club and a
OL,11,Fsmall community," said another member.
OL,13,FThe club was formed in 1947, but it
OL,14,Fisn't often in the limelight.
OL,16,FSo what's it done for Ystradfellte?
OL,18,FCloe Smith, chair of Ystradfellte YFC,
OL,19,Fsaid: "Not many people know about
OL,20,FYstradfellte, but they do now.
