OL,7,F"We don't do as many competitions as
OL,8,Fother clubs. We are more sort of
OL,9,Fcommunity-based. I think because of
OL,10,Fthat, that makes us stand out a bit
OL,11,Fmore than other clubs. But we are a
OL,12,Fsmall club with a big heart."
OL,14,FIts recent summer tractor run raised
OL,15,F#18,000 for Great Ormond Street
OL,16,FHospital, and they hold two every year.
OL,18,FThose who have been involved for many
OL,19,Fyears are proud of the club's journey
OL,20,Fsince it started.
