OL,7,FYstradfellte YFC member Emyr Morgan
OL,8,Fsaid being a part of the club has
OL,9,F"brought me out of my shell".
OL,11,FHe continued: "You get thrown in at
OL,12,Fthe deep end. But you get to know
OL,13,Feverybody from Powys as a county then.
OL,15,F"You get to meet hundreds if not
OL,16,Fthousands of different people. When we
OL,17,Fdo different activities, you learn new
OL,18,Fskills - from carpentry, to welding,
OL,19,Fto stock judging. And from an
OL,20,Fagricultural background, you need it
OL,21,Fall."
